'''聖救恩教堂'''（{{lang-hr|Crkva Sv. Spasa}}<ref>{{cite book | last=Soldo | first=Josip Ante | title=Vrlika - Monografija| publisher=Viatoni | location=Šibenik | year=2001 | language=hr | isbn=953-98670-0-2}}</ref>）是位於[[克羅埃西亞|克羅埃西亞]][[弗爾利卡|弗爾利卡]]市中心西北8公里处的一座[[前罗曼式建筑|前罗曼式]][[教堂|教堂]]<ref>{{cite journal | ref = harv | url = http://hrcak.srce.hr/index.php?show=clanak&id_clanak_jezik=137844 | language = en,hr | title = Sv. Spas na vrelu Cetine i problem westwerka u hrvatskoj predromanici | first = Miljenko | last = Jurković | journal = Starohrvatska prosvjeta | volume = III | number = 22 | date = 1995 | pages = 63–64, 75 | accessdate = 2013-02-26 | issn = 0351-4536 | publisher = Museum of Croatian Archaeological Monuments | location = Split}}</ref>。教堂位于[[采蒂納河|采蒂納河]]沿岸，修建於9至10世紀時期<ref name="vrlika-hist">{{cite web | url = http://www.vrlika.hr/podstranice/povijest.html | title = Povijest | trans_title = History | work = Official site of Vrlika | language = hr | accessdate = 2013-02-26 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130218110336/http://www.vrlika.hr/podstranice/povijest.html | archivedate = 2013-02-18 }}</ref>。之后，它屡遭外族人的破坏<ref name="vrlika-hist"/>。

这座教堂在克罗地亚占有非常重要的地位，因为它是唯一一座保存至今的建于[[東西教會大分裂|東西教會大分裂]]前，并且有[[钟楼|钟楼]]的教堂。

